<div class="container">
        <div class="placard-sidebar">
            <h3>Build meaningful relationships</h3>
            <p class="hilitd">We're here to help your diners feel good, and most importantly, <em>do</em> good just by trying out <strong id="sidebar_restaurant_name"></strong></p>
            <h5>Here's how it works again:</h5>
            <br>
            <p><strong>1).</strong> You share you're a "Buy One, Feed One" establishment and pick a dish to donate.</p>
            <p><strong>2). </strong> Supporters from nonprofits give $1 or greater online for your dish.</p>
            <p><strong>3). </strong> 100% of purchases go straight to the need, and we report monthly on groups you met.</p>
            <p>This costs you $100/mo and we apply a 50% discount until we <strong>prove</strong> we can send you <strong>at least 8 groups</strong> per month. That's typically a 4x-6x return on your investment. Cancel anytime.</p>
